UID: ZEP-SRS-1-35
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Defining a thread stack at compile time
STATEMENT: >>>
The Zephyr RTOS shall provide a mechanism to define a thread stack of a specified size at compile time.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: ZEP-SYRS-15
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: ZEP-SYRS-16

