UID: ZEP-SRS-1-15
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Passing parameters to a thread entry point
STATEMENT: >>>
When a thread is created, the Zephyr RTOS shall pass a defined set of parameters to the thread's entry point function.
<<<
