- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: ZEP-SYRS-17

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: ZEP-SRS-1-17
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Assigning a thread name
STATEMENT: >>>
The Zephyr RTOS shall provide an interface to assign a name to a thread.
<<<
