UID: ZEP-SRS-1-18
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Retrieving a thread name
STATEMENT: >>>
The Zephyr RTOS shall provide an interface to retrieve the name of a thread.
<<<
